  <brief_title>Developing and Validating a Food Frequency Questionnaires (FFQ) for the Vegan Population in Israel</brief_title>
  <official_title>Developing and Validating a Food Frequency Questionnaires (FFQ) for the Vegan Population in Israel</official_title>
  <sponsors>
